<%= link_to '<i class="project-info-link fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>'.html_safe, '#myModal', 'data-bs-toggle' => 'modal', 'data-bs-target' => '#tenziessModal' %>


<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="tenziessModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="tenziessModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-fullscreen">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="tenziessModalLabel"> Tenziess </h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="row modal-body">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          A dice game where the objective is to roll 10 dices that are all the same number.

          To play the game, start by clicking on any dice to "hold" it.
          When you click the "Roll" button, the held dice won't change its value.
          Keep rolling and holding the dice with the same number until all 10 dice display the same number.

          Once you hold the last dice with the same number as the rest, you've achieved "Tenzies"!
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div style="padding:62.5% 0 0 0;position:relative;">
            <iframe
              src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/933214315?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479"
              frameborder="0"
              allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write"
              style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;"
              title="Tenziess App"
            >
            </iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
